.TH MYSTRNCPY 3 "September 2025" "libmyutils" "Library Functions Manual"
.SH NAME
mystrncpy \- copy at most n characters of a string
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <mystrfunctions.h>
.PP
.BI "int mystrncpy(char *" dest ", const char *" src ", int " n );
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B mystrncpy
function copies at most
.I n
characters from the string pointed to by
.I src
to
.I dest.
If
.I src
is shorter than
.I n
characters, the remainder of
.I dest
is padded with null bytes.
.SH RETURN VALUE
Returns the number of characters copied.
